runtime = swayfx eww fuzzel mako swaylock-effects swaybg flameshot foot yazi thunar xdg-desktop-portal-wlr xdg-desktop-portal-gtk playerctl python3 iw nm-connection-editor kira-desktop-audio kira-desktop-fonts kira-desktop-portal

